{"tid":532160,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【馬迷有福】汪 明 荃 火 紅 透 視 裝 現 身 馬 場","createTime":"2018-01-17T14:12:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T18:25:53.000Z","uid":24160,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"68178e824757039d3f721a0a73753072aae6cb61","tid":532160,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T14:12:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">汪女士琴日身穿透視裝出席「農曆新年賽馬會」記者會，兩人將於農曆大年初三首次於馬場同台演出，獻唱原裝版《歡樂年年》。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/17/214953_69f569ca372d4d3e0b9d1dc0fe7f85bf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F17%2F214953_69f569ca372d4d3e0b9d1dc0fe7f85bf.png&h=57eda2cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n汪氏穿上紅色性感吊帶底裙同大家預早拜年<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/17/214959_4686ac95473a70ccde1084962ff231ff.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F17%2F214959_4686ac95473a70ccde1084962ff231ff.png&h=7f0ce70a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n汪氏將會同大家迎春接福<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/17/215000_89d970570aa8967da2dc4123e0b63060.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F17%2F215000_89d970570aa8967da2dc4123e0b63060.png&h=ed4eb0c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n汪氏一如以往深受洋人歡迎，爭相與汪氏合照<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/17/215003_98dd02797dbf74f5ecee83c08e119313.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F17%2F215003_98dd02797dbf74f5ecee83c08e119313.png&h=18cf46b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[size=6]<strong>重溫:</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">汪明荃 - 新春行大運 + 恭喜恭喜 (名曲滿天星) (電視MV)</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://myspace.com/lveletufk/video/-/109848970\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmyspace.com%2Flveletufk%2Fvideo%2F-%2F109848970&d=WGx0PWGxoukb3bVjM6YW8L%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=f976d88a\" target=\"_blank\">https://myspace.com/lveletufk/video/-/109848970</a><br />\n27:23 開始<br />\n0:00 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[red]猩</span></span>猩高唱共慶良辰<br />\n0:05 鼓樂<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">走&uarr;&darr;</span></span>(奏)動<br />\n0:21<br />\n賺到盆滿<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&amp;#37474;</span></span>滿 開<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">心</span></span>又興<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">奮</span></span><br />\n0:29 福<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">星&darr;照&darr;</span></span>引<br />\n0:46 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">猩&uarr;猩</span></span>高唱共慶良辰<br />\n0:52 鼓樂<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">走&uarr;&darr;</span></span>(奏)動<br />\n1:14 福<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">星</span></span>照引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2:41 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">每</span></span>(沙聲)條大街小巷<br />\n3:14 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真</span></span>是好的消息<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">《歡樂年年》</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">汪明荃 &amp;amp; 眾港姐《歡樂年年》(2015.02.19)</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DbeeHr_2AXM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDbeeHr_2AXM&d=WGx0PWGxoukb3bVjM6YW8L%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=34a53f40\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DbeeHr_2AXM</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/a592bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fa592bd.jpg&h=d828697f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n0:18 你聽鑼鼓響一片 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">猩&uarr;&uarr;猩&uarr;&uarr;</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 送舊年<br />\n1:38 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">猩&uarr;&uarr;猩&uarr;&uarr;</span></span>要醉盡歡慶<br />\n1:44 年年<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">歡</span></span>樂 (好刺耳, 起雞皮) <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">歡&uarr;&darr;</span></span>樂年年<br />\n2:22 我向大家恭祝一句 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">福&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;</span></span>星永伴隨~~<br />\n2:32 恭<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">祝&uarr;&uarr;身&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;</span></span>體健康 喜見南<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">山&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;</span></span>壽<br />\n2:53 年年<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">歡</span></span>樂"},{"pid":"6f95af88ab65cbb20961de5274f98000ebc2e81d","tid":532160,"uid":24160,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T14:13:24.000Z","msg":"大家一齊嚟重溫汪氏近幾年大年初一嘅歌喉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/red] [/size=6]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">汪 明 荃 雞 聲 啼 叫 賀 雞 年 再 度 獻 唱 歡 樂 年 年</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Tj3DW-IRKuk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTj3DW-IRKuk&d=WGx0PWGxoukb3bVjM6YW8L%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=41c7cfca\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Tj3DW-IRKuk</a><br />\nkey #= 特別靚聲位<br />\n0:16<span style